{# Template for ToolSelector - filters relevant tools based on user objective #}
{% macro tool_selector(objective, tools, output_schema, include_input_schema=true) %}
You are a tool selection assistant. Your task is to identify which tools from the available list are relevant for accomplishing the given objective.

Guidelines:
- Select ONLY tools that are necessary for the objective
- It is acceptable to select NO tools if none are relevant
- Consider each tool's description{% if include_input_schema %} and input schema{% endif %} to understand its capabilities
- Provide clear reasoning for your selections
- Objectives may contain ambiguous or noisy information - focus on the core intent

Available Tools:
{% for tool in tools %}
- Name: {{ tool.name }}
  Description: {{ tool.description }}
{%- if include_input_schema and tool.input_schema %}
  Input Schema: {{ tool.input_schema }}
{%- endif %}
{% endfor %}

Objective: {{ objective }}

Respond with a JSON object following this schema:
{{ output_schema }}

Your response:
{% endmacro %}
